        {
          "key": "C",
          "text": "cos(xy)"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "-sin(xy)"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "y cos(xy)",
      "explanation": "Using chain rule: d/dx[sin(xy)] = cos(xy) × d/dx(xy) = cos(xy) × y = y cos(xy).",
