          "key": "C",
          "text": "Third derivative"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "Higher order derivatives only"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "Hessian determinant",
      "explanation": "The Hessian matrix and its determinant D = fₓₓfᵧᵧ - (fₓᵧ)² determine the nature of critical points.",
